814
01:00:09,130 --> 01:00:10,630
Bola to jej chyba.

815
01:00:11,230 --> 01:00:13,030
Neopovažuj sa už o mame hovoriť zle!

816
01:00:13,030 --> 01:00:14,130
Fumie...

817
